data.description: New Year | New Home! This house is such a treat! Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath home that's just so cozy! As you step into and through the entry way, you'll immediately fall in love with this charming abode. The kitchen is a sweet treat for any chef, equipped with all the appliances you need to whip up your favorite treats. There is a comforting feeling in the openness of the heart of this home all while highlighting the split bedroom plan. You're just a short trip away from grocery stores, dining options and Ocala shopping. This home is looking for its next owner to embrace all of it's magic all year round. Don't wait - schedule a tour today!
